Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.primitive.map.scalars

Class IntToLongMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.primitive.PrimitiveCollection
      • com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.primitive.map.PrimitiveMap
        • com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.primitive.map.scalars.IntToLongMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.esotericsoftware.kryo.KryoSerializable, PrimitiveScalarMap, Initializable, NamedObject, Countable, Sized, CompressibleCollection
    public final class IntToLongMap
extends PrimitiveMap
implements PrimitiveScalarMap
    A map from int keys to long values. Supports typical map functions:

    Access

    • get(int)
    • put(int, long)
    • remove(int)
    • increment(int)
    • clear()

    Keys and Values

    • keys()
    • values()
    • entries(EntryVisitor)
    • containsKey(int)

    This class supports the hashCode() / equals(Object) contract and is KryoSerializable.

    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
    See Also:
    PrimitiveMap, KryoSerializable
